Package: AMPLE
Title: Compilation of the 'AMPED' and 'PIMPLE' 'shiny' Apps for Stakeholder Engagement and Harvest Strategies
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Finlay Scott <finlays@spc.int>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Finlay",
           family = "Scott",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "finlays@spc.int")
Description: Compilation of the 'AMPED' and 'PIMPLE' 'shiny' applications for stakeholder engagement in developing fisheries harvest strategies. The package is not that useful on its own but provides common functionality including plots, stochasticity options, life history options and a simple surplus production model.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
  shiny (>= 1.3.2)
Imports:
  ggplot2 (>= 3.2.1),
  dplyr (>= 0.8.3),
  tidyr (>= 1.0.0),
  shinyjs (>= 1.0),
  magrittr (>= 1.5)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
